{"tid":150312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Uber 5名司機非法載客取酬罪成","createTime":"2017-03-10T02:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T06:46:29.000Z","uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e75b9a82323e19c2b5f25e790ba71cfcc4afa575","tid":150312,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T02:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c15f85f36f5445b11bbfe911097cbe43060c6c","tid":150312,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T02:48:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170310/56408275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170310%2F56408275&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=bef54bd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170310%2F56408275&h=a04e72e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170310/56408275</a><br />\n<br />\n5名Uber（優步）司機被控「駕駛汽車以作出租或取酬用途」及「沒有第三者保險而在道路使用車輛」罪，代表他們的資深大律師包樂文以司機與乘客之間沒有合約式關係，以及質疑條文沒有足夠彈性處理新科技作抗辯。裁判官今裁定5人全部罪成。<br />\n<br />\n5名被告陸振邦（43歲）、陳鍵豐（29歲）、劉均榮（53歲）、梁愷信（34歲）及陳子麟（40歲）。"},{"pid":"c06f2c8d949bb8b684a58a5eccf46d3e99e009f7","tid":150312,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T02:49:09.000Z","msg":"玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd838502dbd079bd9dc5071c7655ca9190b37be","tid":150312,"uid":3406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T02:50:08.000Z","msg":"唔敢告uber,淨敢告司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a08ad1c37178ae0bbf856ef368357dcd77c1753","tid":150312,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T02:52:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔敢告uber,淨敢告司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquo