ass=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你問下好多的士果條港區人大老姑婆肯唔肯？"},{"pid":"ef37fc3b2accbdd00876c5a2506191da18816325","tid":150312,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係澳洲住表示從來無local 會搭的士（機場同受傷去醫院除外）<br />\n搭uber係common 到再不過既野<br />\n真心唔明點解香港會覺得有問題<br />\n只不過係多一種交通工具<br />\n無人會覺得係咩搶生意<br />\n你9巴同新巴都係2 間公司競爭既喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港一個的士牌值幾百萬</blockquote><br />\n譚惠珠家族有百幾個呢d牌"},{"pid":"7712a8c676e1c9ab66febcb06168c9595aef34f0","tid":150312,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee5f1a0372d27ab7545568487ca54f0bea16cf27","tid":150312,"uid":23536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:00:59.000Z","msg":"香港真係有錢人既天堂<br />\n窮撚真係要諗下技術移民"},{"pid":"db202b55b091ecd460c48503bc6412651ba5b953","tid":150312,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:03:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為痰胃豬</blockquote><br />\n係得你留意到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家繼續坐的士狗<br />\n香港市民表示兜路黑的濫收車費冇影響生活繼續支持"},{"pid":"01e3f02e16eebbbff77752f04b592e500a4201e2","tid":150312,"uid":20237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:06:18.000Z","msg":"判左坐？"},{"pid":"2862651a5436e0a2a21b8dc6e1fdb4b26f11f4f5","tid":150312,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:08:16.000Z","msg":"冇搭的士好耐，希望大家盡量唔好搭"},{"pid":"7893a0229e65d59ac69d97a6c046d1752325770b","tid":150312,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:15:06.000Z","msg":"Gogovan 可以做到被投資，可見跟本唔係乜技術、保險、安全、收錢問題，全因班車行佬嘈。<br />\n<br />\n個牌上到去664萬你話依家俾UBER入黎分呢舊豬肉? 就算擺明係新科技幫助市民普羅大眾又如何? <br />\n<br />\n正如你要樓價跌，咁你又知唔知邊個叫&quot;林奮強&quot;? 行會成員、佢手上有幾多層樓? 咁嘅政府其實係不思進取，等緊爆大獲野。"},{"pid":"87836a2aac8e252c8b1a5e038a5f5e6ec37f3f21","tid":150312,"uid":20237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:19:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講左咁耐，究竟佢地判咩</span></span>"},{"pid":"1faf1cabcae9a3d299351689ca71facc5eeeced5","tid":150312,"uid":78515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:27:27.000Z","msg":"創辛科技<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n施政報告<br />\n<br />\n(四) 創新及科技<br />\n<br />\n54. 創新及科技（創科）不是口號，而是提高香港經濟和社會發展速度的新動力。"},{"pid":"787062b653a210f403daf9b4252d0d12a13d4b5e","tid":150312,"uid":11331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:35:19.000Z","msg":"仆街落地獄啦譯惠珠<br />\n我call實uber<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29013917d638305e987f7165338bc2e1523d3983","tid":150312,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:50:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>創辛科技<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n施政報告<br />\n<br />\n(四) 創新及科技<br />\n<br />\n54. 創新及科技（創科）不是口號，而是提高香港經濟和社會發展速度的新動力。</blockquote><br />\n又話要創新科技<br />\n轉過頭又打壓uber<br />\n明明科技改變世界<br />\nD老屎忽係不思進取<br />\n<br />\n係香港講科技創新真係得啖笑<br />\n幾十年小學學電腦要黎俾接觸新科技 學打文書<br />\nD友番屋企就拎黎msn icq打機<br />\n話要全地區wifi 根本就唔撚駛 香港上網好撚平又快<br />\n根本依個攻府科技創新根本就通通失敗"},{"pid":"665795b83d7120365beb940d6b20efb144a68a2a","tid":150312,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:52:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講左咁耐，究竟佢地判咩</span></span></blockquote><br />\n一萬+停牌一年+充公電話"},{"pid":"d66a8fd41f92759a630745a1b75a86903c6123af","tid":150312,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:54:24.000Z","msg":"其實點解英國又無事？"},{"pid":"b0948954e0290d6b48fd2bb3019ca42c4c0ba14f","tid":150312,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim